From bf63a2355cd9f2c7643e99a6014ae38910d10d77 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 00:46:20 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Own browser editing chords
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Five chords knock upon the pane,
the live tab answers each refrain.
Bindings, menus, shells stand still—
the browser gets the keyboard will.
---
